OL,3,CShock as ability cafe faces closure
OL,5,FA cafe in Millisle which only employs
OL,6,Fthose with disabilities is facing
OL,7,Fclosure next month, with fears staff
OL,8,Fwill not be able to find another job.
OL,10,FThe 'Ability Cafe' opened less than
OL,11,Ftwo years ago as part of a
OL,12,Frefurbishment of the historic
OL,13,FBallycopeland Windmill in Co Down.
OL,15,FPeople who work in the cafe say news
OL,16,Fof its potential closure has come as a
OL,17,F"complete shock".
OL,19,F"I'm absolutely gutted," Jacqueline
OL,20,FAdeoye told UTV. "We've become more
OL,21,Flike a family than workmates.
