OL,5,FA letter sent to Jo from the
OL,6,FDepartment for Communities said:
OL,7,F"During 2023-24 it emerged that USEL
OL,8,Fcould no longer continue to service
OL,9,Fthe Windmill and Ability Cafe at
OL,10,FBallycopeland without being
OL,11,Fsubsidised... due to budget
OL,12,Funcertainty beyond this year, the
OL,13,FDepartment is not in a position to
OL,14,Fcommit to providing a subsidy."
OL,16,FUTV has contacted both USEL and the
OL,17,FDepartment and is yet to receive a
OL,18,Fresponse.
